{"tid":2308274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果A1: 炒40人滅《刺針》　中國組總辭　怒捲劈炮潮　 有線新聞崩壞","createTime":"2020-12-01T18:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T02:10:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"12bc5e384664d44abd11c94527d2a6d47fa1c893","tid":2308274,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/128102446_10159660292422448_8344338425919505307_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=uIgMunmzg_MAX-gXWcF&amp;_nc_oc=AQlE9vRSSkx4uGP_ihR2WcToBHxZUgtuEnNk93shZK1m6EFbahrWVBf4zQZpmyMHaYQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=b95c93a56a44135b1c23275326596ee3&amp;oe=5FEB4AA4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F128102446_10159660292422448_8344338425919505307_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DuIgMunmzg_MAX-gXWcF%26_nc_oc%3DAQlE9vRSSkx4uGP_ihR2WcToBHxZUgtuEnNk93shZK1m6EFbahrWVBf4zQZpmyMHaYQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3Db95c93a56a44135b1c23275326596ee3%26oe%3D5FEB4AA4&h=65d827fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有線寬頻（1097）2017年由邱達昌等商人入主後，經營路向及新聞部方針多番收緊。有線昨再向新聞部開刀，裁減40名員工，其中屢獲獎項的專題組《新聞刺針》被「滅組」。事件引起員工激憤，有線中國組10名員工總辭，港聞16名編採員工辭職明志，批評高層「一手摧毀有線新聞部」。財經及編輯組主管亦遞信離職，有線新聞部頃刻間流失大量人才。有線訂戶亦群情洶湧，指一定「Cut台」，感慨其竟自閹高質素節目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/JMSP5GU7XJGPFNEALQQHF3KESQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FJMSP5GU7XJGPFNEALQQHF3KESQ%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2Wipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=10ea818a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FJMSP5GU7XJGPFNEALQQHF3KESQ%2F&h=d7243750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/JMSP5GU7XJGPFNEALQQHF3KESQ/</a>"},{"pid":"02ab5c0ea1725b45faa74a5a01a0d768d2cfa02f","tid":2308274,"uid":232157,"like":